rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Since many Nopon is merchant,
is Nopon tendency to think about
efficiency in everything.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0002
rows.name: That also manifest in Nopon food.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Use lots of oil, fry quick on strong fire.
Then food done.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Food ready quickly, and full of nutrient.
Very efficient, very Nopon cooking way.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Rododo personally good at making
Lightly Fried Rice while reading
historical document.

rows.label: tlk42300013_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Of course, this also mean precious
historical documents get covered in oil.
